item.title: Coffee Review: Five Star Strong Cold Brew
item.description: Introduction I’ve decided to write a coffee review. I have zero qualification to do so, but the fact that my blood is 75% caffeine helps. This is going to be the first of a series of reviews on the odd coffee beverages I consume to summon enough energy to get through the workday. The subject of this review is Five Star Strong Vanilla Cold Brew. I picked this up from my local grocery store this morning, after seeing it around for a while.
